## 🔮 향후 확장

### Phase 2: 데이터베이스 연동

```freelang
use ORM;
let orm = ORM.create({
  type: "postgresql",
  host: "localhost",
  database: "enterprise_platform"
});

orm.define("users", { id, email, role });
orm.insert("users", { email: "user@example.com", role: "admin" });
```

### Phase 3: 인증 강화

```freelang
let token = Security.createJWT(payload, "secret");
let verified = Security.verifyJWT(token, "secret");
```

### Phase 4: 배포

```bash
# Docker
docker build -t enterprise-platform .
docker run -p 3000:3000 enterprise-platform

# Kubernetes
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
```

